negotiator.analysis

Class BidPointTime

  • java.lang.Object
    • negotiator.analysis.BidPoint
      • negotiator.analysis.BidPointTime
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class BidPointTime
extends BidPoint
    Specialized version of a BidPoint for the case that there are two agents. In this case, the time of offering the bid can be recorded.
    Author:
    Alex Dirkzwager
    See Also:
